5 ways to do more with conversations with the WhatsApp Business App

There’s so much you can do with the WhatsApp Business app to help you work smarter, strengthen relationships with customers, and grow your business.

 

With the WhatsApp Business app, you can:

  1. Attract new customers and drive engagement
  2. Make a great first impression with customers
  3. Communicate one-on-one with your customers throughout the purchase process
  4. Respond instantly to incoming messages, assist sales, and manage your customer communication
  5. Increase sales with features that help you showcase your products and services

“Now, we route every inquiry we receive via various online channels to our WhatsApp Business number. And most customers who contact us directly on WhatsApp do so with the intent to buy.”

 

Sakinah Ali, Owner, Pia Saronde

If you haven’t already, download the WhatsApp Business app, and discover all the features built to help your business succeed.
